  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you would be targeted by an attack or jutsu you unleash a wave of bright light to disorient your opponent.</p><p>All creatures within 10 feet of you must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, creatures take 2d8+2 fire damage and are Blinded until the start of your next turn. On a successful saving throw, creatures take half damage and suffer no further effects. Against all non-blinded creatures, you treat your AC as +3 higher until the start of your next turn.</p>",
